name: Swarm
reason:
The BZZ token provides users with access to data relay and storage services, and compensates node operators for these services.

It is the native token that powers Swarm, a peer-to-peer network of nodes that collectively provide a decentralised storage and communication service. This system is economically self-sustaining due to a built-in incentive system which is enforced through smart contracts on the Ethereum blockchain.
